grammar PetriNet (pn)
root PetriNet

PetriNet:
  'petrinet' id=ID <nsp> ':' <nl>
    <ind>('transitions:' <nl> <ind> transitions+=Transition+ <unind>)? <unind><nl>
    <ind>('places:' <nl> <ind> places+=Place+ <unind>)? <unind><nl> <nl>;

Place:
  'place' name=ID ('tokens' tokenCount=INT)? <nl>;

Transition:
  'transition'<nsp> ':' <nl><ind>
    ('input' input=ID <nl>)?
    'from' <nsp> '[' (from+=[Place] (',' from+=[Place])*)? ']' <nl>
    'to' <nsp> '[' (to+=[Place] (',' to+=[Place])*)? ']'<unind> <nl>;

terminal ID:
  /[a-zA-Z]\w*/;

terminal INT:
  /\d+/;
